# ✨ Commit Summary (50 chars max)


# 📝 Detailed Description
# - What changed?
# - Why was this change necessary?
# - How does it improve the project?


# 🎯 Type of Change (uncomment one)
# feat:     New feature
# fix:      Bug fix
# docs:     Documentation update
# style:    Code formatting/styling
# refactor: Code restructuring
# perf:     Performance improvement
# test:     Testing updates
# chore:    Build/tooling changes


# 📋 Related Issues
# Fixes #
# Relates to #


# ✅ Testing
# - [ ] Tested locally
# - [ ] All tests passing
# - [ ] Documentation updated


# 💡 Notes
# Additional context or breaking changes


# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# MTTGG Commit Template
# Lines starting with '#' will be ignored
# First line: Brief summary (50 chars)
# Second line: Blank
# Remaining lines: Detailed description
